WEBVTT

00:08:00.223 --> 00:08:02.252
I am proof

00:08:02.276 --> 00:08:09.004
that unconditional love and respect
can not only save,

00:08:09.028 --> 00:08:12.069
but it can transform lives.

00:08:13.226 --> 00:08:17.694
Here is a wonderful image
of one of my rescuers, Andy, and I

00:08:17.718 --> 00:08:19.590
taken just last year.

00:08:20.080 --> 00:08:22.641
Ten years after the event,

00:08:22.665 --> 00:08:25.009
and here we are, arm in arm.

00:08:27.559 --> 00:08:29.677
Throughout all the chaos,

00:08:29.701 --> 00:08:32.541
my hand was held tightly.